Package com.example.flashcardsystent.data

Class ClassicResult

java.lang.Object
com.example.flashcardsystent.data.ClassicResult
public class ClassicResult extends Object
Entity storing the result of a completed classic flashcard session. Includes performance statistics such as number of correct/incorrect answers, the hardest card, and session timestamp.
